-======
-An implementation of the [Bukkit](https://hub.spigotmc.org/stash/projects/SPIGOT/repos/bukkit) plugin API for [Minecraft](https://minecraft.net/) servers, currently maintained by [SpigotMC](http://www.spigotmc.org/).
